snippet.title: Rocket Your Friends - Ninjump Dash
snippet.description:
Use the Rocket Power Up to win realtime multiplayer races with your friends in Ninjump Dash. 
NinJump Dash is a realtime, multiplayer racing game featuring your favourite characters from NinJump, the mega-hit game enjoyed by millions of players around the world.  

Available now on IOS and Android Worldwide
